track.name: Tightrope

artist.name: Stevie Ray Vaughan and Double Trouble

comments: It shows all the energy, depth of understanding and experience of blues roots music. He continues to expand the space of modern blues guitar. He’s deserved one of the most virtuosic performers of contemporary blues-rock.
...love it.....walking the tightrope everyday and every night....sing with your guitar stevie.....
Stevie plays this right from heart!!! As he always did!!
straight forward - exactly what I need these days...
this is SRV and DT at their best! pure Texas Blues Rock.  no hendrix riffs srv bieng srv
Awesome! Just what the Dr. ordered for a Saturday.
essential and what for a tight band
Can't get any better than this!
sure glad we have the music, R.I.P. SRV
